# Naval Expansion Pack
# Naval vessels and harbor infrastructure for vanilla DINO factions
#
# Companion to warfare-aerial: an "extension" pack that ADDS base mechanics
# (naval units + harbors) without replacing base-game factions. Modeled on
# packs/warfare-aerial/pack.yaml.

id: warfare-naval
name: Naval Warfare Expansion
version: 0.1.0
framework_version: ">=0.1.0 <1.0.0"
author: DINOForge
description: |
  Naval warfare expansion adding seafaring vessels to vanilla DINO factions.

  Compatible with vanilla DINO — adds content without replacing base game factions.
  Pairs with the warfare-aerial expansion: together they provide the base aerial
  and naval mechanics that themed total conversions (e.g. warfare-starwars) can
  optionally build on.

  Content features:
  - Naval vessels: scout skiffs, war galleys, and heavy warships
  - Uses standard vehicle unit classes mapped to vanilla movement

# Schema 'type' enum has no "extension" member; "content" is the additive-content
# tier (same as warfare-aerial). The "extension" intent is carried by
# classification: engine_extension and the tags below.
type: content
classification: engine_extension

tags:
  - extension
  - naval
  - warfare

depends_on: []
conflicts_with: []

loads:
  units:
    - units/naval_units.yaml


