# Aerial Expansion Pack
# Fantasy aerial units and airfields for vanilla DINO factions
#
# Adds flying units (griffon riders, pegasus cavalry, wyvern scouts) and
# airfield infrastructure (aviary, wyvern roost, ballista tower) to base game.

id: warfare-aerial
name: Aerial Warfare Expansion
version: 0.1.0
framework_version: ">=0.23.0 <1.0.0"
author: DINOForge
description: |
  Fantasy aerial warfare expansion adding flying units and airfields to vanilla DINO factions.
  
  Compatible with vanilla DINO - adds content without replacing base game factions.
  
  Content features:
  - 12 aerial units: griffon riders, pegasus cavalry, wyvern scouts, hippogriff knights,
    harpy raiders, dragon whelps, phoenix hatchlings, cloud giants, roc patrols,
    storm crow ambushers, celestial messengers, and shadow wing strikers
  - 6 airfields: aviary (tier 1), wyvern roost (tier 2), griffon tower (tier 2),
    phoenix nest (tier 3), dragon cave (tier 3), and cloud citadel (tier 4)
  - Anti-air defenses: ballista tower, thunder cannon, mage tower (anti-air spells)
  - 3 aerial doctrines: sky dominance, cloud strike, and aerial superiority

  Units use the DINOForge Aviation subsystem (aerial: config, behavior_tags: [Aerial]).

type: content

depends_on: []

loads:
  units:
    - units/aerial_units.yaml
  buildings:
    - buildings/airfield_buildings.yaml
  doctrines:
    - doctrines/aerial_doctrines.yaml
  # stats/ deferred until aerial_buffs.yaml has valid overrides (empty list fails validation on ReloadPacks)


